  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div>\n\t\t\t<p><i>Prerequisite: Prerequisites: The ability to cast at least one spell</i></p>\n\t\t\t<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You have practiced casting spells in the midst of combat, learning techniques that grant you the following benefits:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You have advantage on Constitution saving throws that you make to maintain your concentration on a spell when you take damage.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You can perform the somatic components of spells even when you have weapons or a <a href=\"https://5e.tools/items.html#shield_phb\"  onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.pHandleLinkMouseOver(event, this, 'items.html', 'phb', 'shield_phb', null)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseLeave(event, this)\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseMove(event, this)\"  ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\" >shield</a> in one or both hands.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When a hostile creature's movement provokes an opportunity attack from you, you can use your reaction to cast a spell at the creature, rather than making an opportunity attack. The spell must have a casting time of 1 action and must target only that creature.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t</div>",
